<inglise> Article 5 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 5 </eesti>
<inglise> On taking up his duties and on ceasing to hold office a member of the Commission or of the Court shall be entitled to: </inglise>
<eesti> Ametisse astudes ja ametist lahkudes saab komisjoni ja Euroopa Kohtu liige: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) an installation allowance equal to two months' basic salary on taking up his duties and a resettlement allowance equal to one month's basic salary on ceasing to hold office; </inglise>
<eesti> a) ametisse astudes sisseseadmistoetust, mis v&otilde;rdub kahe kuu p&otilde;hipalgaga, ning ametist lahkudes &uuml;mberasumistoetust, mis v&otilde;rdub &uuml;he kuu p&otilde;hipalgaga; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) reimbursement of the cost of removal of his personal effects and furniture, including insurance against ordinary risks (theft, breakage, fire). </inglise>
<eesti> b) h&uuml;vitist oma isiklike asjade ja m&ouml;&ouml;bli kolimise kulude katteks, sealhulgas kindlustuse tavariskide (vargus, purunemine, tuli) vastu. </eesti>
<inglise> If his term of office is renewed he shall not be entitled to any of the allowances set out in this Article. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui isik ametisse tagasi nimetatakse, ei saa ta k&auml;esolevas artiklis s&auml;testatud toetusi. </eesti>
<inglise> Nor shall he be so entitled if he is appointed member of another institution of the Communities, if that institution has its provisional seat in the town where he was fomerly required to reside by reason of his office and if at the time of the new appointment he has not already effected his resettlement. </inglise>
<eesti> Toetusi ei saa ta ka juhul, kui ta on nimetatakse ametisse m&otilde;nes teises &uuml;henduste institutsioonis, kui selle institutsiooni ajutine asukoht on linnas, kus ta pidi varem seoses ametikohustuste t&auml;itmisega elama, ning ta ei ole uue ametissenimetamise ajaks sealt veel &auml;ra kolinud. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 6 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 6 </eesti>
<inglise> A member of the Commission or of the Court required in the course of his duties to travel away from the provisional seat of his institution shall be entitled to: </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjoni v&otilde;i Euroopa Kohtu liikmele, kes peab ametikohustuste t&auml;itmisel oma institutsiooni ajutisest asukohast mujale reisima: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) reimbursement of travelling expenses; </inglise>
