<eesti> b) h&uuml;vitatakse majutuskulud (&uuml;ksnes tuba, teenindus ja maksud); </eesti>
<inglise> (c) a subsistence allowance of bfrs 750 for each complete day of absence; for journeys outside Europe the allowance shall be raised to bfrs 1250. </inglise>
<eesti> c) makstakse p&auml;evaraha 750 BFR iga eemalviibitud t&auml;isp&auml;eva eest; reiside eest v&auml;ljapoole Euroopat v&otilde;ib seda suurendada 1250 BFRni. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 7 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 7 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> For three years from the first day of the month following that in which he ceases to hold office, a former member of the Commission or of the Court shall receive a monthly transitional allowance equal to 40 % of the basic salary which he was receiving when he ceased to hold office if he has served for less than two years, to 45 % of such basic salary if he has served for more than two but less than three years and to 50 % in other cases. </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjoni v&otilde;i Euroopa Kohtu endine liige saab ametist lahkumise kuule j&auml;rgnevast kuust alates kolm aastat igakuist &uuml;leminekutoetust, mis moodustab 40% tema ametist lahkumise aja p&otilde;hipalgast, kui ta t&ouml;&ouml;tas asjaomasel ametikohal v&auml;hem kui kaks aastat, 45% nimetatud p&otilde;hipalgast, kui ta t&ouml;&ouml;tas seal kaks kuni kolm aastat ning 50%, kui ta t&ouml;&ouml;tas kauem. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Entitlement to this allowance shall cease if the former member of the Commission or of the Court is reappointed to office in one of the institutions of the Communities or upon his death. </inglise>
<eesti> &Otilde;igus seda toetust saada l&otilde;peb, kui komisjoni v&otilde;i Euroopa Kohtu endine liige nimetatakse tagasi ametisse m&otilde;nes &uuml;henduste institutsioonis, v&otilde;i tema surma korral. </eesti>
<inglise> In the event of reappointment, the allowance shall be paid up to the date of taking up his duties; in the event of death the payment for the month in which death occurred shall be the last. </inglise>
<eesti> Tagasinimetamise puhul makstakse toetust kuni ametisseastumise kuup&auml;evani; surma korral makstakse viimane toetus selle kuu eest, mil ta suri. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> If, during this three-year period the person concerned takes up any new gainful activity, the amount by which his gross monthly remuneration (i. E. Before deduction of taxes) together with the allowance provided for in paragraph 1 exceeds the remuneration, before deduction of taxes, which he was receiving as a member of the Commission or of the Court under Articles 2, 3 and 4 (1) shall be deducted from the allowance. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui asjaomane isik asub asub nimetatud kolme aasta jooksul uuele t&ouml;&ouml;le v&otilde;i tegelema ettev&otilde;tlusega, arvestatakse nimetatud toetusest maha summa, mille v&otilde;rra tema igakuine brutot&ouml;&ouml;tasu (enne maksude mahaarvamist) koos l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud toetusega &uuml;letab makse maha arvestamata t&ouml;&ouml;tasusid, mida ta sai komisjoni v&otilde;i Euroopa Kohtu liikmena artiklite 2, 3 ja artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 kohaselt. </eesti>
<inglise> In calculating the amount of remuneration received for the new activity, all forms of remuneration shall be included, except those representing reimbursement of expenses. </inglise>
<eesti> Uue t&ouml;&ouml; v&otilde;i ettev&otilde;tluse eest saadava t&ouml;&ouml;tasu arvutamisel v&otilde;etakse arvesse iga liiki t&ouml;&ouml;tasu, v&auml;lja arvatud kulude katteks makstav tasu. </eesti>
<inglise> 4. </inglise>
<eesti> 4. </eesti>
<inglise> On the date when he ceases to hold office, on 1 January of each year thereafter and in the event of any changes in his financial situation, a member of the Commission or of the Court shall declare to the President of the institution in which he was previously employed all forms of remuneration received for his services, except those representing reimbursement of expenses. </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjoni v&otilde;i Euroopa Kohtu liige esitab ametist lahkumise kuup&auml;eval, iga sellele j&auml;rgneva aasta 1. jaanuaril ning oma varalise seisundi iga muutuse korral selle institutsiooni juhile, kus ta varem t&ouml;&ouml;tas, deklaratsiooni k&otilde;ikide oma tegevuse eest saadavate t&ouml;&ouml;tasude kohta, v&auml;lja arvatud kulude katteks makstavad tasud. </eesti>
<inglise> Additional remuneration legitimately received by the former member in the course of his duty as a member of the Commission or of the Court shall not be deductible from the transitional allowance. </inglise>
<eesti> T&auml;iendavaid t&ouml;&ouml;tasusid, mida komisjoni v&otilde;i Euroopa Kohtu endine liige oma t&ouml;&ouml; k&auml;igus &otilde;igusp&auml;raselt sai, &uuml;leminekutoetusest maha ei arvestata. </eesti>
<inglise> This declaration must be made in good faith and shall be treated as confidential. </inglise>
